			<span id="id10ab" class="tags">
					{&nbsp;<span><a href="../../../eat/tag/kitchen%20equipment/#selected-tag"><span>kitchen equipment</span></a></span>&nbsp;}
			</span>
		</span></div>
		<div><p style="float:left"><img src="/pictures/carafe.jpg" alt="" /></p>


	<p>Amazon has a <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0001FZB12/qid=1138067732/ref=br_lf_outlet_12/103-3593959-0685404?n=734106&#38;s=outlet&#38;v=glance">good price</a> on this carafe, which reminds me of the beautiful Swedish one Uncle Ted gave me last year. Carafes are an excellent way to keep your coffee or tea hot without turning bitter as fast as they will in a heated coffee pot. This one comes in gray and blue as well, but I prefer the green!</p></div>
